{"name":"Teamwork Feats","pages":[{"sort":100000,"name":"Intro","type":"text","_id":"3ijJhjtkmhl808Af","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p><em>“The sight of people working together, no matter their aim, has ever warmed my heart. Little else gives me such hope for a better future.” —Sinclair, Scholar of Secrets</em></p><p>Tactical coordination can be the crucial difference between success and failure when lives are on the line. This can be as simple as communicating efficiently, or as convoluted as devising elaborate schemes and executing complex martial maneuvers in tandem. While many adventurers assist their fellow party members by contributing their solo skills, some take team synergy a step further. Teamwork feats grant shared benefits to adventurers who train together.</p><p>Teamwork feats are class, general, or skill feats, but always involve two or more actors and possess an added Teamwork entry. This Teamwork entry lists an added benefit applicable if each other involved actor also possesses that specific feat; such allies are referred to as “teammates”. Teamwork feats with the class trait can be taken by any class—including via class feats granted by multiclass archetype feats, such as the fighter archetype’s Basic Maneuver—and gain the class trait associated with the appropriate class.</p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":200000,"name":"Teamwork Feats List","type":"text","_id":"YbsFWVX7nfBWenzt","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.RPfFm4qtHdqrQeKz]{Banter}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.O3E2AdCDS5GWVWyp]{Behind Me}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.iKJ7K6TBILQhlGbC]{Blended Spell}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.QPlsAehaZfvBVZjj]{Charging Assault}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.ICrmvD6LKBwTO6IR]{Coordinated Guard}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.P79yttpPqnJyeHho]{Distant Shield}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.GlIEkPHv6b7FPhGg]{Get Back!}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.54O3MouegtghAnlX]{Helpful Redirection}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.ceqUd6GC9j2RFDGe]{High and Low}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.fKXBXvWDU5etOK43]{Impart Shield}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.KyN4o2lU2jSHC4HB]{Many Hands Make Light Work}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.xNK7UURCo81IDtla]{Pincushion}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.FxyEW1l1qCzlZ130]{Redirect Shot}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.zxuAZ9w1Ag6Xn1UQ]{Saving Hand}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.0tnvHKf7eCG7Z6gn]{Slice and Dice}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.A52t3sYXa8wpJrg2]{Tandem Climbing}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.to3FW8lJqio9s6E6]{Terrifying Emphasis}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.kySXTuqrneZ4zsRr]{Twist the Arm}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.4uSERVm9HyayxaKy]{Two-Handed Delivery}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.c4ohAlejdX3XzCBi]{Up You Get!}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-feats.ixiGjOKRVGO5IQZB]{Watch Your Step}</p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"defaul